text: Starfucker is the name of an indie-electronica band from Portland, Oregon. Starfucker may also refer to: * Starfucker (album), an album by the band * "Star Star", song originally named "Starfucker" on the 1973 album Goats Head Soup by The Rolling Stones * "Starfuckers, Inc.", song by Nine Inch Nails * "Starfucker", a song by Willam Belli from The Wreckoning * Starfuckers, Italian rock band
